speech: A blood group checkup camp was organized by students of Aashayein group in October 2016.
The first TEDx talk in any RTU affiliated college was conducted in JECRC on 25th March 2017 wherein 10 international speakers talked to our students.

A two-day national conference RTDEEE-2016, (Recent Technological Developments in Electronics & Electrical Engineering) was organized in August 2016 where the keynote speaker was Prof. Majid Jamil, Head, Dept. of EE, Jamia Milia Islamia.
